verify GNU Make version is 3.80 or newer

$ make --version
GNU Make 3.81

- ISO/ANSI C compiler needed 
- tar required


download the source code from 
https://www.postgresql.org/ftp/source/

$ cd Downloads/
a directory called postgressql-9.6.2 will created
$ cd postgresql-9.6.2/
$ cd ls 
aclocal.m4  configure     contrib    doc             HISTORY  Makefile  src
config      configure.in  COPYRIGHT  GNUmakefile.in  INSTALL  README

#CONFIGURATION

./configure

